item.description: The next walking meetup is Saturday, April 7, 2007 at 11:00 am . This week we'll meet at Broadmoor Wildlife Sanctuary at 280 Eliot St. Needham, Ma 01760. This is an Audubon trail and is a beautiful, serene spot for a walk. There is an abundance of wildlife to enjoy and has approximately 8 miles of trails. There is a $4 admission fee to the sanctuary. Please note there is also a $1 FEE payable to the organizer to cover membership costs. Thank you and I look forward to seeing you all on Saturday. We will also gather after the walk for lunch at a local restaurant.
